column2: SELECT   m.id as [id], str(m.ra,#,#) AS ra, str(m.dec,#,#) AS dec,   str(sp.modelMag_u,#,#) as u,str(sp.modelMagErr_u,#,#) as err_u,      str(sp.modelMag_g,#,#) as g,str(sp.modelMagErr_g,#,#) as err_g,     str(sp.modelMag_i,#,#) as r,str(sp.modelMagErr_i,#,#) as err_i,        str(sp.modelMag_r,#,#) as r,str(sp.modelMagErr_r,#,#) as err_r,   sp.plate, sp.fiberid, sp.mjd, sp.z, sp.zwarning,  str(pp.z,#,#) as photo_z, pp.zErr into mydb.listMgIIphot_t3 from MyDB.listMgIIphot AS m                         OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS po ON n.objid=po.objid     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON sp.objID=po.objID         LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ pp ON pp.objID = po.objID           WHERE (pp.z >= #)
